oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: I Saw Your Face In The Moon ; Slippin Around - Ernest Tubb performance
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance of I Saw Your Face In The Moon, written by Otis Elder, and performed by Ernest Tubb. Performance of Slippin Around, written by Floyd Tillman, and performed by Ernest Tubb, Red Foley, Margaret Whiting, and Jimmy Wakely. Both are possibly live radio performances.
